OL,6,F"Since my appointment in December
OL,7,F2024, I have met over 2000 officers
OL,8,Fand staff in stations across the force
OL,9,Farea, to understand their roles and
OL,10,Flisten to their views, challenges and
OL,11,Fideas. I will continue to spend time
OL,12,Fwith staff and officers, to understand
OL,13,Fwhere support is needed to protect our
OL,14,Fworkforce and improve morale.
