OL,6,F"Officer numbers will continue to be
OL,7,Fboosted through the Government's
OL,8,FNeighbourhood Policing Guarantee, an
OL,9,Finvestment into neighbourhood policing
OL,10,Fwhich will support the increase of
OL,11,Fneighbourhood officers in years to
OL,12,Fcome and alleviating the pressure on
OL,13,Four frontline.
OL,15,F"I want every member of the
OL,16,Forganisation to feel confident that
OL,17,Ftheir wellbeing is taken seriously and
OL,18,Fthat they are being properly
OL,19,Fsupported. I am committed to ensuring
OL,20,Fofficers know that we are listening
OL,21,Fand feel valued and supported."
